detail_desc: Thin tights with an elasticated waist.
Thong briefs in cotton jersey with a wide lace trim at the top. Low waist, lined gusset, narrow sides and a string back.

Striped shirt in premium cotton with a narrow turn-down collar and French front. Long sleeves with adjustable buttoning at the cuffs, a yoke at the back and a rounded hem. Slim fit with narrow shoulders and a tapered waist for a fitted silhouette.
Cable-knit polo-neck collar in a soft cotton blend containing some wool. Fleece lining front and back.

Shirt in an airy cotton weave with a turn-down collar, open chest pocket and yoke at the back. Long sleeves with a tab and button and adjustable buttoning at the cuffs, and a rounded hem. Regular Fit – a classic fit with good room for movement and a gently tapered waist to create a comfortable, tailored silhouette.
Cardigan in a soft, fine-knit viscose blend with dropped shoulders and long sleeves. No buttons.
5-pocket slim-fit jeans in washed, superstretch denim for maximum mobility with an adjustable, elasticated waist, zip fly and button, and narrow hems.
Short, straight-cut dress in a patterned crêpe weave with long sleeves. Opening with a button at the back of the neck and a seam at the waist. Unlined.
Shorts in sweatshirt fabric with wide elastication and a drawstring at the waist and side pockets. The cotton content of the shorts is organic.
Sports tights in fast-drying functional fabric with wide ribbing to hold in and shape the waist. Concealed key pocket in the waistband.

Satin jumpsuit with a gently draping wrapover front, concealed button at the front and elasticated seam with a detachable tie belt at the waist. Long sleeves with buttoned cuffs, a concealed zip at the side and straight wide legs.
Shorts in soft, stretch denim with hard-worn details, an adjustable elasticated waist and zip fly and press-stud. Fake front pockets, real back pockets and raw-edge, frayed hems.
Jumper in a soft, rib-knit cotton blend with a boat neck, long, wide sleeves with ribbing at the cuffs, and wide ribbing at the hem.
Short trenchcoat in soft Tencel™ lyocell twill with decorative shoulder tabs, a small stand-up collar and draped lapels. Side pockets and a tie belt at the waist. Unlined.
Boxer shorts in cotton jersey with short legs, an elasticated waist and lined front.
Lined balconette bikini top with underwired, lightly padded cups, draping at the front, detachable, adjustable shoulder straps and an adjustable metal fastener. Side support and a silicone trim.
Fully lined bikini bottoms with a mid waist and medium coverage at the back.
Short yoga top in fast-drying functional fabric. Wrapover front with an opening at the top, open section at the back, long sleeves and gathers in the sides.
Treggings in superstretch twill with an elasticated waist, fake front pockets and real back pockets.
Off-the shoulder top in a jacquard weave with a double flounce at the top, narrow shoulder straps at the front and long sleeves. Visible zip at the back and a seam with a flounce at the hem.
Top in woven fabric with narrow shoulder straps, a V-neck front and back and decorative straps at the back. Lined.
Cardigan in soft, fine-knit cotton with sequined embroidery and buttons down the front. Ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Short, straight-cut dress in slub jersey made from a modal and cotton blend with a gentle V-neck and narrow shoulder straps with decorative tie details at the top.
Tulle skirt with a glittery elastic waistband. Lined.
Short-sleeved, round-necked T-shirt in jersey made from a cotton blend.
Gloves in a soft, fine knit. Fleece lining.
Glittery Alice band with two padded hearts. The hearts are decorated with reversible sequins.
Short, sleeveless dress in airy chiffon with elastication and a frill trim at the top, narrow shoulder straps and an elasticated seam at the waist. Jersey lining.
Fully lined, patterned bikini bottoms with a high waist.

Sleeveless, knee-length dress in pleated jersey with a sheen. Round neckline with a V-shaped opening and decorative bar-shaped bead at the back, an elasticated seam and detachable tie belt at the waist, and a laser-cut hem.
Set with a hat, scarf and gloves in a soft fine knit. Double-layered hat with a small appliqué on the turned-up hem. Gloves with ribbed cuffs.
Knee-length sports shorts in fast-drying functional fabric with elastication and a concealed drawstring at the waist, and a key pocket in the waistband. Unlined.
Metal Alice band with fabric and imitation leather appliqués and a decoration in the shape of a unicorn horn.
Trousers in woven fabric with a high paper bag waist, side pockets, detachable tie belt and tapered legs.

Set with a top, leggings and hairband in soft cotton. Sleeveless, A-line top in woven fabric with a flounce at the top that continues back over the shoulders, and an opening and button at the back of the neck. Leggings in soft jersey with an elasticated waist. Hairband in jersey with a decorative bow at the front and elastication at the back.
Short off-the-shoulder top in an airy weave with a sheen. Elastication at the top, long sleeves and elastication and a flounce at the cuffs and hem.
Short-sleeved polo shirt in soft cotton piqué with a collar and button placket.
5-pocket jeans in washed stretch denim with a regular waist, zip fly and button, and skinny legs.
T-shirt in patterned jersey.
Cap in cotton twill with a motif on the front and an adjustable plastic fastener at the back.
Swim shorts in a patterned weave with an elasticated drawstring waist, fake fly, side pockets and short legs with slits in the sides. Soft mesh inner shorts.
Long-sleeved dress in a jacquard knit with a fastening at the back, seam at the hips and a glittery tulle skirt. Partly lined.
Shirt in a cotton weave with a collar, buttons down the front, a yoke with a pleat at the back and long sleeves with buttoned cuffs.
Jacket in a patterned cotton weave with a collar and buttons down the front. Flap chest pockets with a press-stud, and long sleeves with an adjustable fastening at the cuffs. Unlined.
Short coat in soft, felted fabric with notch lapels, a detachable tie belt at the waist, diagonal front pockets and sewn-on tabs at the cuffs. No fasteners. Lined at the top.
T-shirt in soft, printed cotton jersey.
Hipster briefs in microfibre and lace with a low waist, lined gusset, narrow sides and cutaway coverage at the back.
Long, pleated top in jersey with a sheen, with long sleeves and overlocked edges at the cuffs and hem.
Shorts in lightweight organic cotton sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets, and contrasting colour trims and side stripes.
Reversible bomber jacket in woven fabric with a sheen. Ribbed stand-up collar, zip down the front, side pockets at the front, and ribbed cuffs. Lined.
Short shorts in stretch cotton twill with a high waist, back pockets and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems.
Long-sleeved top in textured-knit jersey made from a cotton blend with ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.

Short dress in a crêpe weave with an open section at the front and a V-neck with a tie detail. Opening with a button at the back of the neck, a concealed zip at the back and long sleeves with narrow elastication at the cuffs. Unlined.
Fully lined swimsuit with a V-neck, narrow adjustable shoulder straps and cups with removable inserts that shape the bust and provide good support.
Fine-knit socks in soft chenille with elasticated tops.

Baby Exclusive. Dungarees in woven fabric with an open chest pocket, straps with adjustable buttoning, and buttons at the sides. Concealed press-studs at the crotch and down the legs (except in sizes 1-4Y), and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems. Lined.
Metal rings in various sizes and designs.
Sleeveless romper suits in soft cotton jersey with a concealed press-stud on one shoulder, short legs and press-studs at the crotch and down the legs.
Sleeveless top in soft, printed jersey with a gently flared, rounded hem.
Sports top in fast-drying mesh with dropped shoulders, long sleeves with thumbholes at the cuffs, and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back. The top is made partly from recycled polyester.
Jumpsuit in pleated jersey with a V-neck, wrapover front and an elasticated seam at the waist with a detachable tie belt. Short sleeves and long wide legs. Unlined.

Fully lined bikini. Triangle top with a decorative bow at the front, narrow adjustable shoulder straps that fasten at the back of the neck and a plastic fastener at the back. Matching bottoms with bows at one side.
Fabric belt with an adjustable metal buckle. Width 3.5 cm.
Shorts in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with a washed look. Elasticated drawstring waist, a text print on one leg, a back pocket and roll-edge hems.
Treggings in stretch, denim-look jersey with an elasticated waist, fake fly, fake front pockets and real back pockets.
Short jumper in a soft, rib knit with a small stand-up collar and long sleeves.

Waist bag in grained imitation leather. The bag is divided into two main compartments with a zip at the top and one zipped outer compartment. Adjustable waist strap. Cotton twill lining. Size approx. 3x12x20 cm.
Trousers in soft, gently draping viscose twill with a high, elasticated waist and detachable tie belt. Side pockets and straight, wide legs.

Ankle-length cigarette trousers in a stretch cotton blend with a zip fly, concealed hook-and-eye fasteners and a regular waist with concealed elastication. Side pockets, fake welt back pockets and tapered legs with creases.
Sleeveless dress in soft, organic cotton jersey with a smocked seam at the waist and narrow shoulder straps with a decorative bow.
Trunks in stretch cotton jersey with flatlock seams, short legs, an elasticated waist and lined front.
Earrings in metal and acetate. Two pairs of larger hoops and two pairs with pendants. Length 4.5-6 cm.
Long-sleeved dress in jersey with a supersoft, brushed finish. Small embroidered detail at the top and an elasticated seam at the waist with a decorative, twisted cord bow and tassels.
Boots in imitation leather with an imitation suede shaft and an adjustable tab with a metal buckle at the top and over the foot. Fleece linings and insoles and patterned soles. Heel approx. 2 cm.
Body in jersey with cut-out sections and a metal ring at the waist, high-cut legs and press-studs at the crotch.
Push-up bras in lace and jersey with underwired, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Adjustable shoulder straps and a hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Ballet pumps with pointed toes and satin linings and insoles.
Pull-on trousers in a cotton weave with an elasticated drawstring waist and side pockets. Tapered legs with seams at the knees and elasticated hems.
Lined triangle bikini top with padded cups and removable inserts that shape the bust and provide good support. Narrow adjustable shoulder straps and an adjustable metal fastener at the back.
Cigarette trousers in woven fabric with a regular waist, concealed hook-and-eye fastener and zip fly. Side pockets, fake welt back pockets and tapered, ankle-length legs with creases.
Fitted vest top in ribbed jersey in a narrow cut at the top.
Straight-cut jacket in woven fabric with a slight sheen. Notch lapels, buttons at the front, flap welt front pockets, a welt chest pocket, and buttons at the cuffs. Lined.

Tunic in soft, washed cotton denim with a collar, concealed buttons at the top, a gathered yoke at the back and open chest pockets. Long, gathered sleeves, wide cuffs with press-studs, a seam at the hips and a wide flounce at the hem.
Straight-cut top in soft sweatshirt fabric with a high, ribbed collar and zip at the top. Dropped shoulders, long, slightly wider sleeves and ribbed cuffs. Soft brushed inside.
All-in-one pyjamas in soft, organic cotton jersey with long sleeves, press-studs down the front and along one leg, and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hems.
Vest top in soft cotton jersey with a print motif on the front.
Straight-cut double-breasted jacket woven in a viscose blend with notch lapels and flap front pockets. Lined.

Base layer set in fast-drying functional fabric with jacquard-patterned sections. Top with long raglan sleeves and ribbing around the neckline and cuffs. Bottoms with ribbing at the waist and hems. The base layer set is designed with the minimal number of seams for a more comfortable fit.
Top in sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton blend with a decoration on the front. Dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem. Slightly longer at the back.
High-waisted shorts in woven fabric with decorative buttons at the front. Zip fly with a hook-and-eye fastener, and fake welt pockets at the back.
KIDS EXCLUSIVE. Trainer socks in a soft, rib-knit cotton blend with elasticated tops. The cotton content of the socks is organic.
Calf-length skirt in an airy, patterned weave with a high, gathered waist and concealed zip in one side. Gathered seam at the hips for added width. Unlined.
Tights in a soft, fine knit with an elasticated waist.
Ankle-length dungarees in cotton denim with buttons at the sides and adjustable straps with metal fasteners. Three-part chest pocket, side and back pockets, and tapered legs.
Lined, non-wired bikini top with adjustable shoulder straps and no fasteners.
Short, 5-pocket shorts in washed denim with hard-worn details. High waist and raw-edge, cut-off hems. The cotton content of the shorts is partly recycled.
Round-necked jumper in a soft, fine-knit cotton and cashmere blend with long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Fitted vest top in a soft, rib-knit viscose blend.

Hoodie in soft sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton blend. Jersey-lined hood with a drawstring at the front, dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside. The polyester content of the hoodie is recycled.
Jumper in a soft fluffy knit with a collar and wrapover V-neck, extra-long balloon sleeves with wide, ribbed cuffs, and ribbing at the hem.
